videos.description: Luke Kennard finds the cutting Amile Jefferson who makes the nice move for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Duke's Jefferson finishes with the nice reverse layup

videos.description: Christ Koumadje sends a huge block to the stands for FSU.
videos.headline: Welcome to FSU's Koumadje block party

videos.description: Frank Jackson gets two defenders in the air with a pump-fake and then drives into the lane for lay-in.
videos.headline: Duke's Jackson attacks the rim and gets the layup

videos.description: Leonard Hamilton talks about his teams struggles but how team will still rebound back in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: FSU's head coach Leonard Hamilton talks about his team's first half miscues

videos.description: Frank Jackson drops defender and then with a wide open look hits 3-pointer for Duke.
videos.headline: Jackson drops defender to the floor, drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Jayson Tatum comes down running for the block and sends it hard off the backboard for Duke.
videos.headline: Duke's Tatum tracks down a block and sends the ball flying

videos.description: Luke Kennard drains the deep 3-pointer as the shot clock is expiring.
videos.headline: Kennard hits the deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Amile Jefferson talks about his play and Frank Jackson talks about the upcoming matchup versus UNC.
videos.headline: Amile Jefferson talks about his last game in Cameron Indoor Stadium

videos.description: Dave O'Brien and Dick Vitale talk about how Frank Jackson was the difference maker in Duke's victory over Florida State.
videos.headline: Dave O'Brien and Dick Vitale break down the play of Duke's Frank Jackson
